<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>
<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-12-05T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-12-05T00:00:00-05:00" n="489" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d489">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">Hopkins Papers</note>
                            <head><hi rend="italic">The President’s Special Assistant</hi>
                                    (<persName corresp="#p_HHL1" type="from"><hi rend="italic">Hopkins</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the British
                                    Secretary of State for Foreign Affairs</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_EA1" type="to"><hi rend="italic">Eden</hi></persName>), <hi rend="italic">and Reply</hi><note n="1" xml:id="d489fn1">The exchange, which was handwritten on a
                                    single sheet of paper, presumably took place during the
                                    quadripartite dinner meeting, <hi rend="italic">ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_733">p. 733</ref>.</note></head>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Cairo</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-12-05">December 5 (?), 1943</date>.]</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p><persName corresp="#p_EA1"><hi rend="smallcaps">Anthony</hi></persName>:—It looks like <gloss target="#t_Buccaneer1"><hi rend="smallcaps">Buccaneer</hi></gloss> is out &amp; our military plans hence
                                will be agreed to tomorrow</p>
                            <closer><signed><persName corresp="#p_HHL1"><hi rend="smallcaps">Harry</hi></persName></signed></closer>
                            <postscript>
                                <p>If so, you have been very generous, but our chances next year
                                    will surely benefit.</p>
                                <p>President has been grand about it all.</p>
                                <p>Note reinforcements (Scotch) just came in!</p>
                            </postscript>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>